99-0650 (La. 4/23/99)

Allen A. TOUCHET v. FIDELITY CASUALTY CO. and Wedge Wireline, Inc. No. 99-C-0650. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Fidelity Casualty Co.; Wedge Wireline Inc.; — Defendants); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Office of Workers’ Compensation District # 4 Number 97-01876; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CA98-1230

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J. not on panel. TRAYLOR, J. would grant the writ.
